    connections:["Harold 'Sonny' White: White's Casimir / ZPE work is exactly the quantum vacuum physics Epstein's 2006 conference was convened to discuss.","TAE Technologies / Trump Media: The 2025 merger places a sitting President's family business inside the fusion sector that Epstein's conference mapped at the elite level."],
    links:[["Wikipedia — Jeffrey Epstein","https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jeffrey_Epstein"],["Wikipedia — Death of Jeffrey Epstein","https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Death_of_Jeffrey_Epstein"],["NPR — Epstein and the Physics Conference (2026)","https://www.npr.org/2026/03/09/nx-s1-5721150/epstein-scientists-physics-virgin-islands-conference"]],
